# Keep paper source files tracked:
# - paper/*.tex (paper, presentation, poster)
# - paper/*.bib (bibliography)
# - paper/style/*.sty (helper packages only)
# - figures/*.png (code-generated figures for papers)
# - Makefile (build system)
# - sweeps/*.yaml (sweep config files)
#
# Local/untracked files (gitignored above):
# - paper/WORKFLOW.md (AI agent instructions)
# - paper/SUBMISSION_CHECKLIST.md (compliance tracking)
# - paper/icml2026-official/ (reference only, do not edit)
